Germany’s Roesler Aims for Tax Cuts Before Elections, Bild Says

-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 
2011-05-25T05:49:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-25/germany-s-roesler-aims-for-tax-cuts-before-elections-bild-says.html
Philipp Roesler,  Germany ’s new
economy minister, plans to reduce the tax burden for middle- and
lower-income groups during the current legislative period,  Bild-
Zeitung  reported, citing unidentified people who attended a
working group meeting with the minister yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
